{"tid":1652340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<第N次> 政府呼籲 : 和平示威者與暴徒割席","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:39:59.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb8e27cb0e70514288e2ac8e0a93934ffd7fc2f","tid":1652340,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">割你老母</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/13/P2019101300797.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F13%2FP2019101300797.htm&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeNzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=fde4a103\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/13/P2019101300797.htm</a><br />\n政府對蒙面暴徒暴力行為表示強烈憤慨<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（十月十三日）對蒙面暴徒再次在全港多區施暴施襲表示極度憤慨；暴徒的行為對市民安全構成極大威脅，嚴重破壞社會安寧，必須予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n　　暴徒明顯針對警務人員進行襲擊，有暴徒以利器割傷警員頸部、圍毆警務人員並嘗試奪取其裝備、向警車投擲汽油彈導致警車着火、向旺角警署投擲多枚汽油彈，並以磚頭等硬物攻擊警務人員，對警務人員安全構成嚴重威脅，令人髮指。特區政府嚴厲譴責暴徒的襲擊行為，警方亦定必全力追究。對有人在網上不斷發放指控警務人員的失實言論，政府發言人呼籲市民須認清事實，以防被誤導。發言人亦向受傷警員致以慰問。<br />\n<br />\n　　暴徒響應近日網上有人策動的所謂「遍地開花」行動，在多區肆意破壞政府及港鐵設施、立法會議員辦事處，以及多間暴徒選定的銀行和商店，不少地方被縱火；有暴徒襲擊其他市民，亦有人針對傳媒機構施襲。有人在多區堵路，癱瘓交通，嚴重阻礙消防和救護工作；更有人向港鐵沙田站路軌投擲雜物和破壞輕鐵路軌，隨時會釀成嚴重意外，威脅乘客及港鐵職員的人身安全。輕鐵下午起因被破壞而須全線暫停服務，多個港鐵站亦要提早關閉，對出行市民造成極度不便，更令市民人心惶惶。此外，有人在黃大仙焚燒國旗，挑戰國家主權，亦涉嫌違反《國旗及國徽條例》。<br />\n<br />\n　　發言人説：「特區政府強烈譴責暴徒的暴力行為，將以最大的決心遏止暴力，亦呼籲參與和平示威的市民與暴徒劃清界線，維護香港法治的核心價值，與政府共同努力回復社會秩序。」<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2019年10月13日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時57分"},{"pid":"6f0a0586edcf09dd70bc0a0a802f9917efb156a0","tid":1652340,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af9453711301e0f351736f87f44d3e9893250e1","tid":1652340,"uid":258068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"[前線][文宣入]用黑警借車反咬政府一口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n真心重要<br />\n輕輕一推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b264b554c718f5faad68a7ea3fb16a4432d4ecb","tid":1652340,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc89021179d998f061ff558363570e8f68fd78b4","tid":1652340,"uid":48531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"割你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f266fc3a3134d27f4738c38cf72d8f1fa525de63","tid":1652340,"uid":46148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"港共正苦：冇棋啦 快D割啦你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f708618e728c4d848fce6e79a0ebeb08d952292","tid":1652340,"uid":23160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:50:40.000Z","msg":"香港警察 集體自殺"},{"pid":"a643e874ff69e6d4d37f98f7725a7a321e66a780","tid":1652340,"uid":202112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r